on PC: 
git status
git add .
git commit -m "Describe what you changed"
git push


on Pi:

cd ~/homebeam
git pull
npm ci
npm run build
sudo systemctl restart homebeam


One last important habit (keep this forever)

Whenever something breaks:

Check browser console first

Fix on PC

git push

git pull on Pi

Restart

That workflow will save you days over time.